{"tid":1228985,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"傷心到訓唔著","createTime":"2019-06-15T19:28:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T19:46:05.000Z","uid":161209,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"432112f1b5ee43346a4d5c2a498b68822e61fd4f","tid":1228985,"uid":161209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T19:28:59.000Z","msg":"有無巴打都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咁迫自己快啲瞓養足精神聽日去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39cd88dbc0257de0dbdf6ba0118671ecc4c227cd","tid":1228985,"uid":98041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T19:29:24.000Z","msg":"訓唔到 唔敢再睇"},{"pid":"5951cfb249c6082ab4024151dc35e6c72d0da9c8","tid":1228985,"uid":184132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T19:29:56.000Z","msg":"想跳想死嘅同我入一入嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1228885\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1228885</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n全部人同我睇左佢"},{"pid":"758476fa5b04e1e126b6d668ae7c8e87dd153fcb","tid":1228985,"uid":161209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39cd88dbc0257de0dbdf6ba0118671ecc4c227cd","tid":1228985,"uid":98041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T19:29:24.000Z","msg":"訓唔到 唔敢再睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T19:31:04.000Z","msg":"越睇越傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7630bcbd39c51777ca5bb3e27f901a7825c80bda","tid":1228985,"uid":262498,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T19:34:24.000Z","msg":"polly:<br />\n有好多人表示呢段時間擔心到瞓唔着，<br />\n冇心機做野亦都休息唔到。<br />\n辛苦大家，以下係少少放鬆方法比大家參考<br />\n<br />\n①放空<br />\n放空成個人，乜都唔好諗，個腦好似白紙咁<br />\n<br />\n②深呼吸<br />\n慢慢吸氣4秒，慢慢呼氣6秒，不斷循環2-3分鐘<br />\n<br />\n③飲水<br />\n淨係飲咖啡奶茶凍野等等，係好易令自己維持煩躁狀態。特別係對住電腦耐嘅巴絲，太多咖啡/提神飲品反而會榨乾精神。<br />\n慢慢飲杯暖水或者室溫清水，飲水可以幫助清除雜念，亦都可以沖走身體裏面嘅雜質。全日黎計可以1-2個鐘一杯水<br />\n<br />\n④執野<br />\n最簡單係執檯面，執房，最常用嘅地方清理左先。全部抹乾淨執乾淨，依次序大小擺好檯面/房間裏面嘅野。<br />\n<br />\n⑤臨瞓聽啲柔和啲嘅歌，會放鬆自己精神壓力，個腦先可以休息<br />\n(個人推介Francesca Battistelli, Hillsong同Bethel Music嘅歌)<br />\n<br />\n⑥唔好屈自己係間房入面，出街行下，去小區食碗豆腐花<br />\n<br />\n⑦安靜諗下呢幾日發生嘅事，所見所聞，到底自己仲有乜野係缺乏 就好襯而家去準備。搵定附近最方便自己嘅交通工具<br />\n<br />\n⑧可以比自己唔開心/內疚/有情緒，但係一定要同自己講要出返黎，轉牛角尖係冇用。有需要嘅一定要搵身邊嘅人或者社工幫手<br />\n<br />\n⑨任何事做最好嘅準備，做最壞嘅打算<br />\n<br />\n[ 養精蓄鋭 ] 瞓唔着/大壓力可以參考下<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1218519\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1218519</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"616a61855a2da77cf18e7a1b577cbdb6677763ab","tid":1228985,"uid":8290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T19:41:47.000Z","msg":"想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c77d9f0f77a1409c51a45f9f638f415908f26896","tid":1228985,"uid":251925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T19:42:28.000Z","msg":"訓唔撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f2635a8a4263923771b201c2877aace4d27e880","tid":1228985,"uid":120676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T19:43:14.000Z","msg":"same here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eb304d1e8d321058ffc1e9767c8414262f731e5","tid":1228985,"uid":65209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T19:44:51.000Z","msg":"好難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b23ce5441011320bb4e42d6402a96158865c34","tid":1228985,"uid":10726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T19:45:50.000Z","msg":"可以嘅咪去打鋪機, 再沖個涼先訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c557ebb90aa78f15b037a55297caf7daab3d915c","tid":1228985,"uid":154089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T19:46:05.000Z","msg":"個心好痛"}]}